original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Church Avenue
text:
New Lots Road, east from Church Ave., seen in the foreground. Building at right, is a 2-story brick at 551 East 98th Street. (The trolley line that once continued east on New Lots, now swings sharply right and goes south one block to Hegeman Ave., then east again along Hegeman Ave).

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
